58c913101f1a5faa20e_270237987_678429676853160_1730009156035624415_n-p-500.jpeg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6256995755a7ea0a3d8fbd11/687a758c913101f1a5faa20e_270237987_678429676853160_1730009156035624415_n-p-800.jpeg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/6256995755a7ea0a3d8fbd11/687a758c913101f1a5faa20e_270237987_678429676853160_1730009156035624415_n.jpeg 1080w" class="img"/></div><div class="author-modal-name"><div class="t-14-500 t-1440-14">Article by </div><div class="t-14-700 t-h-140">Alex Davidovich</div></div></div><div class="author-modal-bio"><div class="t-16-500">Alex Davidovich is an entrepreneur with over a decade of experience in content production and product design. Having built and scaled creative service businesses from the ground up, he brings hands-on expertise and trusted insight to every topic he writes about.</div></div><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/alex-davidovich?utm_source=share&amp;utm_campaign=share_via&amp;utm_content=profile&amp;utm_medium=ios_app" target="_blank" class="in-link-author w-inline-block"><div class="footer-social-icon footer-social-icon-new footer-social-icon-new__ar w-embed"><svg width="100%" height="100%" viewBox="0 0 14 15" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
